translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「夜の間には雨も上がるみたいだし、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It seems the rain will stop during the night,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日はもう寝てしまって、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so let's just go to sleep now,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 明日は早朝から出発することにしましょう」
いそいそとナギが寝床の用意を終え、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagi busily finished preparing the bedding,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: さっさとその場に寝転がる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and quickly lay down right there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: たまには久し振りに一緒の布団で――」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: How about sleeping together under the same futon for once in a while—"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「駄目よ、子供じゃないんだから」
二人はそれぞれの布団の中に潜り込んだ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The two of them slipped into their respective futons.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王の子達はみんな、強いわよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: All the Demon King's children are strong."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ま、心配なのは分かるけどね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Well, I do understand why you’re worried though."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後で会ったとき、笑われないように、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So later, when we meet them again, we won’t get laughed at,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私達もちゃんと、強くならないとね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: we have to properly become stronger too."
"We absolutely have to protect those kids...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私達の、弟と妹達……大事な家族だもん……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our little brothers and sisters... they’re precious family to us..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はーい、明かり消すねー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Okay, I’ll turn off the light now."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゆっくりと体を休め、眠りについた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: slowly rested their bodies and fell asleep.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それぞれがそれぞれの冒険を順調に続けていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Each of them was steadily continuing their own adventure.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは順調にハニーインザスカイを
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were steadily progressing through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は順調にハニーインザスカイを
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You all were steadily progressing through Hanny in the Sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 雲で出来た大きな橋の上に何かがいるのが見えた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you saw something on a large bridge made of clouds.
"I don’t have a good feeling about this..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ににんにん、主君殿、気をつけてでござる」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ninin nin, my lord, please be careful."
"W-what is it... could it be enemies...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なにかな、なにかな？　ワクワク」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What could it be, what could it be? Exciting."
